01.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13124209/Aloha-Shoe_Profile-View_NoLaces-747x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb25 747w\"></a></p><p>Take the existing S-Works Recon gravel shoe and add laces, and you get the new S-Works Recon Lace. With a welded mesh/TPU and Dyneema upper that has been stripped of any hardware, in addition to a more customize able fit, the shoe also gets lighter at 280g (claimed, size 42).</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13124204/Aloha-Shoe_Bottom-View_LB.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13124204/Aloha-Shoe_Bottom-View_LB.jpg\" alt=\"S-Works Recon Lace SPD compatible gravel shoe\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13124204/Aloha-Shoe_Bottom-View_LB.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13124204/Aloha-Shoe_Bottom-View_LB-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13124204/Aloha-Shoe_Bottom-View_LB-800x450.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13124204/Aloha-Shoe_Bottom-View_LB-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13124204/Aloha-Shoe_Bottom-View_LB-768x432.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13124204/Aloha-Shoe_Bottom-View_LB-696x392.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/13124204/Aloha-Shoe_Bottom-View_LB-1068x601.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/